Data::Perl::Number::MooseLike(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation Data::Perl::Number::MooseLike(3)

NAME

Data::Perl::Number::MooseLike - data::Perl::Number subclass that simulates Moose's native traits.

VERSION

version 0.001009

SYNOPSIS

    # you should not be consuming this class directly.

DESCRIPTION

This class provides a wrapper and methods for interacting with a boolean. All methods are written to emulate/match existing behavior that exists with Moose's native traits.
